The Truth is this : I cannot stay Flaring in Sunshine all the Day : For , entrae Nous , We Hellish Sprites , Love more the Fresco of the Nights ; And oftener our Receipts convey In Dreams , than any other Way
more the Fresco of the Nights
Go then this Evening , Master Carvel , Lay down your Fowls , and broach your Barrel
Friends some half a Dozen , The Colonel , and my Lady's Cousin

Barbadoes Waters for the Close ; Till Hans had fairly got his Dose : The Colonel toasted to the best : The Dame moved off , to be undrest : The Chimes went Twelve : the Guests withdrew : But when , or how , Hans hardly knew
From thence was carried off to Bed : John held his Heels , and Nan his head
